modeling example:
   *dice, p(6) = a > 1/6*
   1p(1) + ... + 5p(5) + 6a = E
   (1-a)/5*15 + 6a = 3 + 3a

   roll dicece 100 times \righarrow 400 \Rightarrow 400/100 = 3 + 3a \Rightarrow a = 1/3

